                <head>160. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>The Subcommittee on Foreign Trade Policy of the House Ways and Means Committee
                    held hearings on private foreign investment December 1–5. Under Secretary of
                    State <persName corresp="#p_DCD1">Dillon</persName>, International Cooperation
                    Administration Director <persName corresp="#p_SJHJ1">Smith</persName>, and
                    Development Loan Fund Managing Director <persName corresp="#p_MID1"
                        >Mcintosh</persName> testified before the Subcommittee December 1. For texts
                    of their statements, see Department of State <hi rend="italic">Bulletin,</hi>
                    December 29, 1958, pages 1056–1066.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
